title: Last.Fm Self Cacher and Viewer
description:
Due to recent last.fm server issues i have created an application to locally back up what you listen to.
Then when these issues are resolved you can submit them to the staff so you don't lose all your scrobbles.
unrar and run application then follow the readme
Readme provided	
Now included an application to view your tracks and if you are on the internet it will show album art
